		<title xml:space="preserve"><![CDATA[[ENG]-HOSTEDTAB- New Generation Gaming Roleplay [0.3.7]]]></title>
		<content type="html" xml:space="preserve" xml:base="https://www.burgershot.gg/showthread.php?tid=2279"><![CDATA[<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">New Generation Gaming Roleplay! By gamers, for gamers.</span><br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">[Take Note: If there were <span style="text-decoration: underline;" class="mycode_u">ever</span> any other servers by the name of New Generation Gaming Roleplay, there are no intentions of being a 'copy' as we would have never been aware. There are many servers on SAMP that may or may not share the same name whether they're on Hosted Tab, or not.]</span><br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">NOW ON HOSTED TAB! </span><br />
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b"><a href="https://discord.gg/6EZNmpzXSm" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="mycode_url">https://discord.gg/6EZNmpzXSm</a></span><br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">ADDRESS: 198.37.123.212:7777</span><br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">A brand new English Medium/Heavy RP server with professional and legitimized administration, very stable economy, multiple jobs, hosted events, rewards up to first 15 hours of active gameplay and more!</span><br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">Factions are looking for members: </span><br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">San Andreas State Police,</span><br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">LSFMD, </span><br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">Government(once a stable playerbase is produced.)</span><br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">Jobs available at the moment are- </span><br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">Weapons Smuggler(Crate orders restricted to illegal factions only.), </span><br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">Cargo Unloader, </span><br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">Courier,</span><br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">Taxi,</span><br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">Mechanic, </span><br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">Pizza Delivery Boy, </span><br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">Crate Smuggler, more are to be added.</span><br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">As for the rewards- </span><br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">5 Playing Hours = 5k Cash. </span><br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">10 Playing Hours = 5k Cash &amp; Car of choice (Restrictions apply. Car choice removed if you already have a car by 10 hours.) </span><br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">15 Playing Hours = 10k Cash.</span><br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">It's all about the fun, getting to know one another, creating a whole new thriving community! We definitely look forward to seeing any of you great &amp; lovely people in either our Discord or our Server. Have a great day, and happy SAMPing!</span>]]></content>
