		<title xml:space="preserve"><![CDATA[Southland Roleplay - Heavy RP]]></title>
		<content type="html" xml:space="preserve" xml:base="https://www.burgershot.gg/showthread.php?tid=2231"><![CDATA[Southland Roleplay is an upcoming roleplay server on SAMP coming out in mid January!<br />
<br />
It's the passion project of players from several well-known heavy roleplay servers who want to keep the English roleplay scene alive on SAMP. It features one of the most advanced scripts that have SAMP as ever seen with a custom overlay, graffiti system, in-game internet, and phone system.  There has truly never been anything like Southland.  This discord has over 1,000 members and could be SAMP's last hope for English roleplay. <br />
<br />
Most importantly it has a staff team that will listen, they've seen the downfall of the other English servers over the years and know the community drives a roleplay server. <br />
<br />
https://discord.gg/zVdSDAHXUa<br />
<br />
https://forum.sl-rp.net/index.php]]></content>
