		<content type="html" xml:space="preserve" xml:base="https://www.burgershot.gg/showthread.php?tid=2225"><![CDATA[<img src="https://img.tpx.cz/uploads/erroripvzadu.png" loading="lazy"  alt="[Image: erroripvzadu.png]" class="mycode_img" /><br />
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">Greetings everyone, Are you looking for SA-MP servers Freeroam ? There you go! :)</span><br />
<br />
Language Servers: <span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">English/Czech/Slovak</span><br />
<br />
Visit our SA-MP Servers :<br />
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">Server 1</span> 0.3.7 Client server:<br />
To connect: <span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b"><a href="samp://play.superparba.eu:7777" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="mycode_url"><span style="color: #ff851b;" class="mycode_color">play.superparba.eu:7777</span></a></span><br />
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">Server 2</span> 0.3DL Client server own <a href="https://youtu.be/gCwuDWwn3LE" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="mycode_url">islands</a> and new story missions:<br />
To connect: <span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b"><a href="samp://dl.superparba.eu:7777" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="mycode_url"><span style="color: #e86e04;" class="mycode_color">Dl.superparba.eu:7777</span></a></span><br />
<br />
Server’s Website: <span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b"><a href="https://superparba.eu/news.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="mycode_url"><span style="color: #ff851b;" class="mycode_color">SuperParba.eu</span></a></span><br />
<br />
Discord: <a href="https://discord.com/invite/VRrtbsCJgb" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="mycode_url"><span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b"><span style="color: #ff851b;" class="mycode_color">https://discord.com/invite/VRrtbsCJgb</span></span></a><br />
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">Why should you play on our game servers?</span><br />
<br />
SuperParba is built on building a community and it's character, in which you can run your own<br />
business, buy properties, companies, be a member of a gang - ride races, fight for territory, take<br />
over warehouses in a unique GANG system. Plenty of various events from the Administration Team such<br />
as Fallout, Sky (street) races, Color Dash, Runners VS Riders, Shooters VS Riders, Random events, Hit &amp; Run,<br />
Tuning events, Derby, Death Events, DM ... will take place every day and are complemented by MEGA<br />
events that take place over several weeks! We have been operating since 2008, the server has gone<br />
through hundreds of full-fledged updates from suggestions for improving the server from the gaming<br />
community! PARTY SERVER with the gamemode RZE 10.1 mode gets right under your skin, such is the<br />
SuperParba!<br />
<br />
- A professional Admin Team, which oversees order, creates fun and helps players with any problem.<br />
If you do not know how to deal with something, use <span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">/ask</span> to send your question directly to the<br />
Administrators and you will receive an answer in a short time.<br />
<br />
- For newbies was added a quick tutorial. For navigation to startup place use the command<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">/tutorial</span>. After completing the tutorial with 0 hours played, the newcomer will get 7 days of<br />
premium classic for free.<br />
<br />
- Players have found a lot of fun, emotions, twists, friends, news and memories during those 12<br />
years. There are even a few real relationships that they got to know at SuperParba. It will be<br />
crazy once they tell their kids. Players are happy to return to our server, so come and join our<br />
family!<br />
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">Thank you for reading.</span>]]></content>
